data.description:
This is a package deal that includes MLS numbers 533286 and 534845; Property ID’s: 103847, 153746, 133507, and 149065.
Discover the ultimate country living experience with this exclusive package deal, encompassing two distinct properties that together boast over 45 acres! This unique offering is complete with a charming single-family home, a single-wide, an above-ground pool, and expansive farmland featuring various outbuildings, barns, stables, and fenced areas for animals. The main residence boasts 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a wood burning fireplace in the living room. The kitchen has built-in appliances and an island that doubles as a breakfast bar. The master bedroom features an ensuite bathroom with dual sinks, tub and separate shower. The single-wide offers a large carport and a well-maintained interior. Don't miss the chance to own this rare piece of Texas countryside! Schedule your tour today!
